To get started you will need to setup the following:

1) Setup the config/database.yml file so that rails can access your databases.
2) Setup the information required in config/heffer.rb
3) Setup teh following email addresses:
  a) orders@<DOMAIN>

x) Navigate to the /private part of the site and setup the following:
  a) A username and password (Optional but highly recommended)
  b) A page titled 'homepage' (Optional will replace default)
  c) A page titled 'returns' (Optional but refered to in dispatch notice)
  d) A page titled 'legal' (Optional)
  e) A page titled 'contact' (Optional)

